# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Havyn Client — Environment Variables
# Copy to `.env` (Vite only exposes vars prefixed with VITE_).
# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Base URL of the API. In development the Vite dev server proxies /api to the
# backend (see vite.config.js), so the default "/api" works out of the box.
# In production set this to your deployed API origin, e.g. https://api.havyn.app/api
VITE_API_URL=/api
